    "description": "TOPDLv2.1 is a part of Gemalto's TOPDL family of Java Cards and offers a comprehensive array of features and options for logical and physical access control applications. TOPDLv2.1 is a highly secure platform for private and public sector smart card deployments implementing Java Card 2.2.2 and Global Platform 2.1.1/2.2 Amdt D specifications with both contact and contactless interfaces. TOPDLv2.1 is ideally suited for markets such as Identity or Security/Access, including one-time password authentication, Public Key Infrastructure (PKI) services, digital transactions and physical access control",
